CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 6, 1960, pg. A9, reads: "After The Ball - Mrs. Morris Fountain, second from left, and her husband, a Frog, entertained several guests at a breakfast following the Frogs' formal last Friday. Left to right: Mmes. Ralph Barnett, Fountain, Katherine Lowery, Cleveland, Ohio; Roger Thomas, Betty Moore, Miss Marilyn Thomas, Mrs. Jody Harris and Mrs. William Nicholson. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Ann Barnett, Miriam Fountain, Katherine Lowery, Helen Ruth Thomas, Betty Moore, Marilyn Thomas, Jody Harris, and Mrs. William Nicholson, seated in Fountain home
